The raw UNSW-NB15 dataset is not stored in this repository because of GitHub file size limits.
To reproduce training, download the UNSW-NB15 CSV files and place them in:

data/external/UNSW-NB15/

Expected files:
UNSW-NB15_1.csv
UNSW-NB15_2.csv
UNSW-NB15_3.csv
UNSW-NB15_4.csv
